caption: The best pudding I’ve ever had in my entire life!!! All of the flavors are delicious. I have a dairy sensitivity and before I could even open my mouth the owner let me know her recipes are vegan! All 6 flavors are vegan & 100% organic dairy free!! YESSSSSS! God is real!! God is GOOD!! Alsoooo, she is such a sweet woman. She really cares about her customers and does what it takes to build lasting relationships with her customers. Not only is Simply Southern a black owned business it’s also woman owned, straight out of NYC! You can’t go wrong with that. ♡ GO ORDER YOURS NOW, you will NOTTTTT regret it. Thank me later.
Amazing Banana Pudding! Would definitely recommend it 😊

Great quality pudding, packaging looks amazing. Real tasty with real bananas and a various different flavors and sizes.I especially loved the chocolate banana pudding! Place your orders,owner is very gracious and friendly.

Amazing! It's really hard to have a favorite when you like and tasted all of them. I'd usually just go for coconut but when I had the other samples I was mind blown. Simply Southern makes you become more open minded. Thank you for a great experience! You definitely have a new customer here for sure.

Coming from someone that doesn't really fancy sweet food.. this product definitely have me reconsidering. It's so good and freshh and natural. Love the banana pudding the best. Actual fresh bananas!! 5 stars across the board!
Great service & tasted amazing so I am definitely a fan!

Simply Southern NYC houses the BEST banana pudding I have ever had the pleasure of tasting!! The pudding comes in a variety of flavors and is just the most sublime dessert experience you will ever have here in NYC. It’s southern, sophisticatedly crafted, sentimentally prepared and just utterly DELICIOUS. You will cry tears of joy while sharing one of these jars (or five of the big jars!!) with the family!

Love, love, love this banana pudding! Its fresh, vegan and the owner is so nice. This pudding is so good, so many varieties. I dont feel bad indulging in Simple Southern because of how natural and good the ingredients are.
Her pudding are AMAZING ! My favorite was the strawberry pudding ! I definitely recommend!!

Seriously, guys, this is the BEST Banana Pudding EVER! It is a must  you definitely need To taste. If you love creamy, rich, light and fluffy banana pudding, this is for you. It’s a huge hit with all my friends  that tried it!

Whitney makes the best vegan pudding I have ever tried. It’ll make you want to finish the whole thing in one sitting. Highly recommended!! Make sure you make that deposit so your order is guaranteed. Make sure you request the coconut-banana flavored one in a medium. You won’t regret it. ;)

U can tell when things are done with tender loving care and this pudding from simply southern is just that!! The perfect amount of sweet, creamy and vegan  I tried original, chocolate, and strawberry all amazing packaging is adorable highly recommend

Simply Southern NYC has the best banana pudding ever. I really loved both flavors that I’ve tried so far. Which were original and pistachio. They have plenty other flavors to choose from. If, your ever in the mood for some good ole southern banana pudding, this is a must try. I promise you, you’ll want more. For, all you who don’t do diary, did I mention it’s totally VEGAN!!! 😋Everyone thank me later 😊

The owner of this business is very kind and caters to her customers. And the pudding is so good, I give it a 5 star, and would Definetly recommend to anyone who loves pudding, would like it for themselves or catered for an event!
